Product description

Everything an ambitious professional needs. Laptop compatible, high on functionality & comfort.The Aristocrat OPP range of laptop backpack is one of the most affordable offerings; yet affords very practical features. These are designed to carry laptops safely while providing ample space for essentials in its multiple compartments. It comes with fabric bottle pocket, padded shoulder strap, padded back panel and a webbing grab handle.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Customers say

Customers find the backpack to be of good quality, offering good value for money, and appreciate its light weight and good looks. They consider it perfect for office use and carrying laptops, though opinions about size are mixed, with some finding it spacious while others say it's very small. The storage capacity receives mixed feedback, with some finding the space good while others say it's not sufficient. The material quality also gets mixed reviews, with some praising the fabric while others describe it as very thin.
